</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All those who responded were very helpful.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Secure and Packed with features</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/boionfire81/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1ded72d94ed09210408c2fcb0d7f3be4?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1ded72d94ed09210408c2fcb0d7f3be4?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/boionfire81/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">boionfire81</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">August 19, 2024</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Honestly, a great plugin. Here\'s why:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Packed with features straight out of the box.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Very secure and constantly kept up to date. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Integrates with alot of other service providers. </li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Hundreds of additional (free &amp; paid) plugins to